%20general%20says%20was%20used%20to%20recruit%20Haitian%20immigrants%20into%20a%20pyramid%20scheme.%3Cp%3ESupreme%20Court%20of%20the%20State%20of%20New%20York%2C%20New%20York%20County%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Leticia%20James%20has%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20crypto%20platform%20NovaTechFx.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20claims%20the%20company%20defrauded%20thousands%2C%20targeting%20immigrant%20and%20religious%20communities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFounder%20and%20%26quot%3BReverend%20CEO%26quot%3B%20Cynthia%20Petion%20called%20her%20investors%20a%20%26quot%3Bcult%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20once%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20financial%20platforms%20on%20the%20market.%20Now%2C%20the%20New%20York%20attorney%20general%20says%20NovaTechFx%20is%20just%20a%20front%20for%20a%20%241%20billion%20pyramid%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Leticia%20James%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcourt-filings%2Fnot_assigned_people_of_the_state_of_v_people_of_the_state_of_complaint_2.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20founders%2C%20Cynthia%20and%20Eddy%20Petion%2C%20in%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accuses%20the%20Petions%20of%20defrauding%20thousands%20of%20investors%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20bringing%20in%20%26quot%3Bover%20a%20billion%20dollars%20by%20promoting%20two%20consecutive%20fraudulent%20investment%20schemes.%26quot%3B%20The%20lawsuit%20also%20names%20as%20a%20defendant%20AWS%20Mining%20Pty%2C%20a%20crypto%20mining%20platform%20previously%20run%20by%20the%20Petions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20NovaTechFx%20was%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F100-fastest-growing-digital-brands-capital-one-travel-geller-grover-2023-1%23financial-services-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efastest-growing%20online%20financial%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20terms%20of%20internet%20traffic.%20The%20company's%20website%20attracted%2012.4%20million%20visitors%20that%20year%20%E2%80%94%20a%20518%25%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovaTechFx%20falsely%20advertised%20itself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bregistered%20hedge%20fund%20broker%26quot%3B%20and%20claimed%20incorrectly%20that%20it%20had%20licenses%20to%20trade%20cryptocurrency%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20accuses%20the%20couple%20of%20targeting%20Haitian%20immigrants%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20recruit%20them%20into%20the%20pyramid%20scheme%20using%20local%20prayer%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20founding%20NovaTechFx%20in%202019%2C%20Cynthia%20Petion%20rebranded%20herself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BReverend%20CEO%2C%26quot%3B%20claiming%20that%20her%20company%20was%20%26quot%3BGod's%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20private%20messages%2C%20she%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bzookeeper%26quot%3B%20and%20her%20investors%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcult%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20join%20and%20follow%20mindlessly%E2%80%A6%20they%20don't%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Petition%20says%20in%20messages%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20%26quot%3BThey%20just%20agree%20with%20everything%20you%20say.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20NovaTechFx%20workers%20created%20flyers%20advertising%20prayer%20groups%20hosted%20by%20the%20company%20with%20slogans%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20team%20that%20prays%20together%20stays%20together%20%26amp%3B%20grows%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Petions%20also%20operated%20the%20NovaTechFx%20website%2C%20which%20the%20lawsuit%20says%20is%20where%20investors%20would%20go%20to%20invest%20in%20cryptocurrency%20through%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20investors%20intended%20to%20use%20for%20trading%20%E2%80%94%20NovaTechFx%20would%20transfer%20the%20funds%20%26quot%3Bto%20a%20payment%20processor%20that%20did%20not%20trade%20cryptocurrency%20for%20NovaTech%20but%20merely%20stored%20it%20in%20NovaTech's%20wallets%2C%26quot%3B%20court%20documents%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AG's%20office%20says%20that%20of%20the%20over%20%241%20billion%20deposited%20through%20the%20website%20from%202019%20to%202023%2C%20NovaTechFx%20only%20actually%20traded%20about%20%2426%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20New%20Yorkers%20were%20falsely%20promised%20better%20lives%20if%20they%20simply%20trusted%20NovaTech%20and%20AWS%20Mining%20with%20their%20money%2C%20but%20it%20was%20all%20a%20lie%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fpress-release%2F2024%2Fattorney-general-james-sues-cryptocurrency-companies-novatechfx-and-aws-mining%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThese%20cryptocurrency%20companies%20targeted%20immigrant%20and%20religious%20communities%20with%20promises%20of%20financial%20freedom%20but%20instead%20stole%20their%20money%20and%20drained%20their%20life%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenold%20Julien%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20Konbit%20Neg%20Lakay%2C%20a%20local%20Haitian%20nonprofit%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20that%20most%20Haitian%20immigrants%20come%20to%20the%20United%20States%20to%20flee%20violence%20and%20don't%20deserve%20to%20be%20taken%20advantage%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thank%20Attorney%20General%20James%20for%20taking%20this%20action%20to%20protect%20all%20New%20Yorkers.%20Konbit%20Neg%20Lakay%20is%20looking%20for%20full%20restitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20lawsuit's%20filing%2C%20the%20NovaTechFx%20website%20has%20displayed%20a%20message%20from%20Cynthia%20Petion%20saying%20the%20company%20experienced%20a%20%26quot%3Bdata%20breach%26quot%3B%20and%20temporarily%20took%20down%20its%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20delighted%20to%20inform%20you%20about%20successfully%20recovered%2086%25%20of%20all%20official%20data%20from%20the%20trading%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20says.%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20enable%20withdrawals%2C%20all%20accounts%20have%20been%20integrated%20into%20a%20new%20domain.%20To%20regain%20full%20access%2C%20please%20log%20in%20using%20your%20exact%20details%20on%20the%20website.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENovaTechFx%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnovatechfx-crypto-trading-platform-lawsuit-scam-leticia-james-new-york-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717927981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66649896e0790490181735ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnovatechfx-crypto-trading-platform-lawsuit-scam-leticia-james-new-york-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NovaTechFx%2C%20once%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20financial%20platforms%2C%20now%20faces%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20says%20it%20stole%20%241%20billion%20in%20a%20pyramid%20scheme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnovatechfx-crypto-trading-platform-lawsuit-scam-leticia-james-new-york-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20longer%20can%20Parliament%20be%20bulldozed%20like%20last%20decade%3A%20Sonia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717927855000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%