3Emore%20details%20than%20anyone%20wanted%20%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20the%20former%20president's%20sex%20life.%20But%2C%20after%20weeks%20of%20testimony%2C%20one%20mystery%20lingered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20of%20the%20prosecutors%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Trump%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20Karen%20McDougal%2C%20a%20former%20Playboy%20model%2C%20while%20his%20wife%2C%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20was%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20that%20McDougal%20and%20Trump%20had%20an%20affair%20was%20not%20new.%20The%20idea%20that%20the%20affair%20took%20place%20while%20Melania%20Trump%20was%20expecting%20a%20child%2C%20however%2C%20had%20never%20been%20previously%20reported.%20The%20prosecutor%2C%20Assistant%20District%20Attorney%20Joshua%20Steinglass%2C%20disclosed%20it%20at%20a%20hearing%20just%20before%20jury%20selection%20began%2C%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20was%20that%20detail%20that%20would%20bolster%20the%20prosecution's%20argument%20that%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-trial-charges-explained-narrative-as-jury-deliberates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilenced%20women%20to%20benefit%20his%202016%20presidential%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20this%20relationship%20occurred%20during%20the%20defendant's%20wife's%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20child%2C%20speaks%20directly%20to%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20defendant%20believed%20the%20story%20would%20be%20damaging%20to%20his%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinglass%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20two%20sources%20with%20knowledge%20of%20McDougal's%20relationship%20with%20Trump%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20got%20the%20detail%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20just%20as%20surprised%20as%20you%20when%20Josh%20Steinglass%20stated%20that%20Melania%20was%20pregnant%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Carol%20He