%221505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20McDougal%20at%20a%20Playboy%20golf%20event%20in%202007%2C%20during%20the%20time%20she%20says%20she%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20Trump.%3Cp%3EChad%20Buchanan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Heller%2C%20Merchan%20relied%20on%20Steinglass's%20error%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-judge-melania-pregnant-testimony-playboy-model-affair-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20ruled%20prosecutors%20should%20not%20question%20McDougal%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20subject%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinglass%20had%20told%20the%20judge%20he%20would%20not%20elicit%20%26quot%3Bthe%20salacious%20details%20of%20the%20affair%2C%20to%20describe%20the%20sexual%20acts%20or%20locales%20of%20their%20liaisons%26quot%3B%20from%20McDougal%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20Trump's%20lawyers%20would%20%26quot%3Bopen%20the%20door%26quot%3B%20to%20it.%20But%20the%20judge%2C%20in%20his%20ruling%2C%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bprejudicial%26quot%3B%20to%20bring%20up%20%26quot%3Bthe%20defendant's%20wife%20was%20pregnant%20with%20a%20child%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20that%20this%20went%20on%20while%20she%20was%20pregnant%20and%20even%20after%20she%20gave%20birth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSteinglass%20misspoke%20about%20Melania%20being%20pregnant%20during%20the%20affair%2C%20and%20Merchan%20relied%20on%20the%20incorrect%20impression%20he%20gave%20when%20he%20talked%20about%20Melania%20being%20pregnant%2C%26quot%3B%20Heller%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20everyone%20has%20previously%20reported%2C%20including%20Karen%20herself%3A%20Karen%20met%20Mr.%20Trump%20at%20the%20Playboy%20Mansion%20when%20they%20were%20filming%20an%20episode%20of%20The%20Apprentice%2C%26quot%3B%20Heller%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20June%20of%202006.%20Barron%20was%20already%20three%20months%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20ultimately%20never%20called%20McDougal%20to%20testify%2C%20so%20the%20timeline%20discrepancy%20wasn't%20raised%20again%20and%20didn't%20become%20the%20subject%20of%20further%20scrutiny%20in%20the%20trial.%20Jurors%20never%20heard%20any%20evidence%20about%20it%20either%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20detail%20ultimately%20proved%20inconsequential%20to%20winning%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%20charged%20Trump%20with%2034%20counts%20of%20falsifying%20business%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20Stormy%20Daniels%20%E2%80%94%20a%20different%20woman%20who%20says%20she%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20him%20%E2%80%94%20to%20unlawfully%20keep%20the%20information%20secret%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinglass%20marshaled%20an%20almost-dizzying%20matrix%20of%20dates%20and%20other%20details%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-lawyer-uses-da-evidence-against-his-client-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20marathon%20five-hour%20closing%20argument%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-trial-verdict-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejury%20convicted%20Trump%20of%20all%2034%20counts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc2c7c15-c00d-4781-bf91-6162039dc149%5C%22%3EMcDougal's%20story%20helped%20explain%20'catch%20and%20kill'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Trump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nydailynews.com%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2Fpresident-trump-used-to-boast-about-having-sex-with-his-friends-wives-devised-calculated-infidelity-plots%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboasted%20about%20his%20infidelity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20general%20terms%2C%20but%20has%20seldom%20publicly%20talked%20about%20McDougal%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20April%20court%20hearing%2C%20Trump's%20lead%20defense%20at