uding%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGoogle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20Subway%2C%20and%20USPS.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20worker%20worked%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcircle-k-green-thumb-industries-weed-florida-gas-stations-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECircle%20K%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20Parker's%20Kitchen%2C%20a%20South%20Carolina-based%20chain%20of%20convenience%20stores%20and%20gas%20stations%2C%20by%20claiming%20shifts%20through%20Shiftsmart.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20worker%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation%20at%20work.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20the%20worker's%20identity%20and%20employment.%20The%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20homeless%2C%20and%20gig%20work%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20kept%20me%20above%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20Shiftsmart%20last%20year.%20I%20needed%20a%20way%20to%20make%20extra%20money%2C%20and%20a%20friend%20turned%20me%20on%20to%20it.%20I%20signed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20go%20to%20Circle%20K%20and%20work%20as%20a%20cleaner%20and%20merchandiser.%20To%20start%20a%20four-hour%20shift%2C%20I%20would%20show%20up%2C%20contact%20the%20manager%2C%20and%20let%20them%20know%20that%20I'm%20here%20to%20assist%20with%20whatever%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20put%20you%20on%20certain%20tasks%3A%20Mopping%20up%20the%20floor%2C%20cleaning%20the%20bathrooms%2C%20restocking%2C%20just%20different%20odd%20jobs%20they%20need%20to%20take%20care%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20other%20jobs%20that%20I%20could've%20gotten%20on%20Shiftsmart%2C%20like%20a%20mystery%20shopper%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20were%2050%20miles%20away%20%E2%80%94%20an%20hour's%20drive.%20You%20could%20take%20them%2C%20but%20then%20you're%20out%20the%20time%20and%20gas%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20shifts%20sit%20unclaimed%20for%20too%20long%2C%20they'll%20entice%20you%20by%20raising%20the%20pay.%20The%20other%20day%2C%20I%20went%20in%20and%20worked%20a%20little%20over%20four%20hours.%20The%20estimated%20pre-tax%20earnings%20would've%20been%20%2457.17%20with%20a%20%2450%20bonus%20because%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20pick%20up%20that%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bonus%20will%20start%20at%20%2410%2C%20for%20example%2C%20then%20they'll%20raise%20it%20up%20to%20%2420%2C%20then%20they'll%20raise%20it%20up%20to%20%2430%2C%20and%20so%20on%20until%20somebody%20takes%20that%20shift.%20You%20get%20paid%20between%2024%20and%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20shift%2C%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20funny%20is%20that%20one%20of%20the%20managers%20for%20this%20Circle%20K%20location%20I%20worked%20at%20through%20Shiftsmart%20noticed%20that%20I%20was%20working%20hard%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20are%20you%20doing%20this%20just%20for%20side%20money%2C%20or%20are%20you%20looking%20for%20a%20full-time%20job%3F%20I%20would%20love%20to%20hire%20you.%26quot%3B%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20her%20up%20on%20it%20and%20start%20working%20there%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShiftsmart%20itself%20has%20technical%20issues.%20Once%2C%20I%20was%20missing%20just%20over%20%241%20of%20my%20pay.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20in%20through%20the%20app%20and%20submit%20a%20request.%20They%20sometimes%20correct%20it%2C%20but%20sometimes%20you%20won't%20hear%20anything%20from%20them.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20keep%20going%20after%20somebody%20for%20%241.17%2C%20but%20that%20adds%20up%20over%20the%20scale%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20who%20could%20be%20experiencing%20the%20same%20thing%20that%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20uses%20a%20ranking%20system.%20They%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Breliability%26quot%3B%20score%2C%20which%20is%20how%20often%20you%20actually%20show%20up%20to%20shifts%20and%20how%20often%20you%20cancel%20shifts%20with%20at%20least%2024%20hours'%20notice.%20They%20also%20have%20an%20%26quot%3Bon-time%26quot%3B%20score.%20That%20goes%20down%20if%20you%20are%20late%20to%20work%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20if%20you%20show%20up%2030%20minutes%20or%20more%20early%20and%20clock%20in%2C%20then%20your%20time%20will%20also%20go%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20that%2C%20at%20the%20pay%20rate%20Shiftsmart%20and%20Circle%20K%20were%20offering%2C%20it%20was%20putting%20me%20further%20into%20a%20hole%20financially.%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20exact%20numbers%2C%20but%20Shiftsmart%20has%20to%20be%20getting%20paid%20by%20Circle%20K%20whenever%20someone%20takes%20a%20shift.%20As%20an%20employee%2C%20I%20can%20make%20more%20money%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20same%20rankings%20and%20compete%20for%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20just%20cutting%20out%20the%20middleman%2C%20in%20other%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20into%20gig%20work%2C%20by%20all%20means%2C%20do%20your%20hustle%20and%20try%20to%20survive%2C%20but%20don't%20get%20stuck%20in%20it.%20Understand%20that%20these%20types%20of%20gig%20jobs%20are%20not%20for%20all%20people.%20If%20somebody%20gets%20hurt%20on%20the%20job%2C%20they're%20not%20covered%20by%20workers%20compensation.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I'd%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShiftsmart%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20worker%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-gig-worker-explains-why-they-wouldnt-do-it-again-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717926122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%