yees%20better%20rather%20than%20relying%20so%20much%20on%20tips%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20a%20Bankrate%20post%20about%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty-five%20percent%20of%20adults%20said%20%26quot%3Btipping%20culture%20has%20gotten%20out%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20Bankrate%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20US%20adults%20who%20always%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-cheap-bad-restaurant-tipping-best-worst-states-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etip%20servers%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20those%20who%20go%20to%20sit-down%20restaurants%20slipped%20from%20the%202022%20survey%20%E2%80%94%2073%25%20said%20this%20in%20the%202022%20survey.%20This%20wasn't%20the%20only%20kind%20of%20tipping%20for%20which%20the%20share%20of%20adults%20using%20these%20services%20who%20said%20they%20always%20tip%20slipped%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20table%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FzqpMs%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20US%20adults%20who%20say%20they%20always%20tip%20the%20following%20people%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8d17535-4fde-4b5c-a566-881c3609207f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20people%20end%20up%20giving%20a%20tip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Rossman%2C%20a%20senior%20industry%20analyst%20at%20Bankrate%2C%20noted%20to%20Business%20Insider%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20people%20end%20up%20tipping.%20There's%20when%20it's%20typically%20expected%2C%20or%20people%20may%20tip%20to%20try%20to%20get%20better%20service.%20Another%20could%20be%20to%20avoid%20feeling%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20we%20tip%20more%20out%20of%20guilt%2C%20like%20they%20flip%20the%20tablet%20around%20and%20you%20feel%20bad%20saying%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERossman%20told%20BI%20that%20Gen%20Xers%20and%20baby%20boomers%20were%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20more%20likely%20to%20say%20there's%20too%20much%20tip%20creep%20and%20tipping%20culture's%20gotten%20out%20of%20control.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20the%20survey%20found%2078%25%20of%20Gen%20Xers%20and%2086%25%20of%20baby%20boomers%20who%20go%20to%20sit-down%20restaurants%20always%20give%20a%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20younger%20Americans%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20tip%20at%20sit-down%20restaurants.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20only%2035%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20who%20go%20to%20sit-down%20restaurants%20are%20always%20tipping%2C%20only%2056%25%20of%20millennials%20who%20go%20to%20sit-down%20restaurants%20always%20tip%20there%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20setting%20where%20I%20feel%20like%20you%20should%20be%20tipping%20every%20time%2C%20ideally%2020%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20this%20backlash%2C%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20added.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20it%20is%20high%20prices%2C%20some%20of%20it%20is%20tip%20creep%2C%20some%20of%20it%20is%20maybe%20just%20people%20feeling%20like%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20go%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Ffactors-affecting-whether-and-how-much-americans-tip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E%20survey%20of%20US%20adults%20conducted%20in%20August%20also%20highlights%20when%20people%20tip.%20That%20survey%20found%2077%25%20said%20service%20quality%20is%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20deciding%20whether%20they%20tip%2C%20and%2018%25%20called%20this%20a%20minor%20factor.%20Almost%20a%20third%20of%20adults%20said%20how%20much%20the%20worker%20or%20workers%20earn%20before%20tips%20is%20a%20major%20factor%2C%2023%25%20said%20social%20pressure%20is%20a%20major%20factor%2C%20and%2023%25%20said%20how%20much%20the%20tip%20will%20end%20up%20costing%20them%20is%20a%20major%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BService%20quality%20is%20by%20far%20the%20most%20cited%20factor%20across%20all%20age%20groups%2C%20but%20younger%20Americans%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20older%20people%20to%20consider%20certain%20other%20factors%2C%26quot%3B%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20adults%20under%2030%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20those%2065%20and%20older%20to%20point%20to%20workers'%20pre-tip%20wages%2C%20social%20pressure%20and%20cost%20as%20major%20factors%20when%20deciding%20whether%20to%20leave%20a%20tip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1d39088-002d-44ed-8c1b-7f0efd5ac67f%5C%22%3EWhen%20to%20leave%20a%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20should%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-to-tip-restaurant-bars-food-delivery-hotel-salon-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etip%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20time%20you%20place%20an%20order%2C%20stop%20in%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-to-tip-uber-hairstylist-housekeeping-delivery-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaircut%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20get%20an%20appliance%20delivery%3F%20Rossman%20said%20his%20advice%20is%20for%20people%20to%20make%20a%20priority%20list%20of%20who%20to%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20this%20is%20especially%20useful%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-tip-workers-around-the-holidays-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholidays%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20pressure%20to%20give%20a%20teacher%20gift%20and%20to%20tip%20the%20trash%20guys%20and%20the%20mailman%20and%20your%20kid's%20daycare%20provider%20and%20everybody.%20If%20you%20can't%20tip%20everybody%2C%20maybe%20at%20least%20prioritize%20who%20really%20went%20above%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Rossman%20thinks%20there%20are%20several%20places%20or%20services%20where%20people%20should%20give%20a%20tip%3A%20at%20a%20hair%20salon%20or%20barbershop%2C%20food%20delivery%2C%20taxis%20and%20rideshares%2C%20and%20sit-down%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20rideshare%20driver%2C%20you're%20paying%20out%20of%20your%20pocket%20for%20gas%20and%20insurance%2C%20and%20if%20people%20aren't%20tipping%2C%20that's%20really%20taking%20a%20chunk%20out%20of%20your%20wages%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20said.%20Similarly%2C%20Rossman%20said%20many%20food%20delivery%20workers%20%26quot%3Bare%20footing%20the%20bill%20for%20things%20like%20gas%20and%20car%20insurance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERossman%20said%20tipping%20for%20coffee%20shops%2C%20food%20trucks%2C%20or%20takeout%20restaurants%20are%20more%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20there's%20a%20big%20distinction%20between%20where%20tipping%20is%20more%20expected%20and%20where%20it%20could%20be%20optional%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20do%20think%20the%20lines%20are%20blurring%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%20businesses%20are%20looking%20to%20customers%20to%20make%20up%20some%20of%20the%20difference%20%E2%80%94%20that%20maybe%20they're%20reluctant%20to%20raise%20prices%20any%20higher%3B%20they're%20looking%20to%20supplement%20their%20employees'%20wages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20sick%20of%20tipping%20culture%3F%20Are%20you%20a%20server%2C%20driver%2C%20hairstylist%2C%20or%20other%20worker%20who%20has%20seen%20fewer%20tips%20lately%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EReach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftipping-culture-restaurant-servers-uber-drivers-giving-fewer-tips