the%20moon%20and%20planets%20from%20the%20quiet%20of%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20remove%20all%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20Tellez%20said%20of%20the%20traffic-restricted%20street.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221265%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%2034th%20Avenue%20Open%20Street%20is%2026%20traffic-restricted%20blocks%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20entirely%20car-free%20plazas%20outside%20schools.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661e845d0b8e1c832cc9e44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22945%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2034th%20Avenue%20Open%20Street%20is%2026%20traffic-restricted%20blocks%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20entirely%20car-free%20plazas%20outside%20schools.%3Cp%3EEliza%20Relman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22faef4d13-8367-4bba-aab7-7b5a196af97d%5C%22%3EA%20'superhighway'%20of%20pedestrians%20and%20bikes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJim%20Burke%2C%20a%20longtime%20pedestrian%20and%20transit%20advocate%2C%20had%20lived%20in%20his%20apartment%20building%20right%20on%2034th%20Avenue%20for%20a%20dozen%20years%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit.%20But%20he%20knew%20virtually%20none%20of%20his%20neighbors.%20In%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20bored%20in%20their%20apartment%2C%20Burke%20and%20his%20partner%20started%20regularly%20playing%20a%20coin-tossing%20game%20in%20the%20street.%20Soon%2C%20neighbors%20and%20kids%20began%20joining%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20Bronx%20and%20the%20Rockaways%20and%20remembers%20that%20as%20kids%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20%26quot%3Bowned%20the%20streets%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20they%20played%20every%20day.%20He%20figured%20adults%20and%20kids%20alike%20should%20have%20that%20same%20experience%20on%2034th%20Avenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20led%20to%20another%20and%20then%20we%20started%20raising%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Burke%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20looked%20out%20their%20windows%20and%20said%2C%20'Oh%20that%20looks%20like%20fun%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20my%20house%20for%20another%20minute.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Doherty-Naranjo%20and%20Burke%20co-founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.34aveopenstreets.com%2Fhome%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E34th%20Avenue%20Open%20Streets%20Coalition%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20used%20the%20funds%20they%20raised%20to%20put%20on%20programming%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0hiring%20yoga%20and%20Zumba%20instructors%20to%20teach%20free%20classes%2C%20volunteers%20to%20lead%20English%20lessons%2C%20and%20even%20enlisting%20doctors%20to%20dispense%20free%20medical%20advice.%20The%20effort%20was%20entirely%20volunteer-powered%20for%20the%20first%2018%20months%20before%20the%20city%20stepped%20in%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20summer%2C%20I%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20doing%20activities%2C%20or%20going%20out%2C%20walking%2C%20kids%20playing%20with%20chalk%20%E2%80%94%20just%20cool%20things%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20when%20growing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yorladiz%2C%20a%20Jackson%20Heights%20native%20who%20regularly%20walks%20her%20four-year-old%20daughter%20up%20and%20down%2034th%20Avenue.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20yoga%20night%2C%20it's%20salsa%20night%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they're%20always%20doing%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20Burke%20can't%20spend%20more%20than%20a%20few%20minutes%20on%2034th%20Avenue%20without%20running%20into%20a%20neighbor%20he%20knows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20this%20superhighway%20of%20kids%20and%20families%20and%20neighbors%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Doherty-Naranjo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20controversy%20on%2034th%20Avenue%20mostly%20concerns%20a%20surge%20in%20mopeds%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20use%20the%20street%20as%20a%20cut-through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShekar%20Krishnan%2C%20the%20councilman%20who%20represents%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20held%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qchron.com%2Feditions%2Fcentral%2Fkrishnan-dot-must-curtail-mopeds%2Farticle_3556fb64-1f90-11ef-a0d4-6b3281da2713.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMoped%20Crisis%26quot%3B%20town%20hall%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20and%20says%20the%20City%20needs%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20redesign%20the%20street%20to%20keep%20mopeds%20off%20of%20it%20and%20create%20safer%20ways%20for%20them%20to%20travel%20on%20other%20streets.%20If%20the%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20is%20going%20%26quot%3Bto%20oversee%20the%20expansion%20of%20public%20space%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20their%20other%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Krishnan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20need%20to%20get%20far%20more%20serious%2C%20and%20ambitious%2C%20and%20creative%20in%20how%20they%20do%20so%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20listen%20to%20the%20communities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20kick%20around%20a%20soccer%20ball%20while%20an%20older%20woman%20walks%20by%20on%2034th%20Avenue%20in%20Jackson%20Heights%2C%20Queens.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661ea0acc442a2f676ea910%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22946%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThousands%20of%20students%20use%20the%2034th%20Avenue%20Open%20Street%20to%20get%20to%20and%20from%20school%20every%20day.%20Many%20use%20it%20as%20a%20place%20to%20hang%20out.%3Cp%3EEliza%20Relman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20and%20O'Doherty-Naranjo%20don't%20want%20to%20ban%20mopeds%20from%2034th%20Avenue.%20They%20recognize%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-drivers-e-bikes-mopeds-danger-traffic-crashes-nyc-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20streets%20often%20aren't%20safe%20for%20moped%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20delivery%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunding%20for%20open%20streets%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20come%20by%2C%20however.%20Across%20the%20city%2C%2083%20miles%20of%20open%20streets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F08%2F11%2Fnyregion%2Fopen-streets-nyc.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edwindled%20to%20about%2020%20miles%20between%202020%20and%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%20DOT%20only%20allots%20%2420%2C000%20a%20year%20for%2034th%20Avenue%2C%20Burke%20said%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20funds%20needed%20to%20operate%20the%20open%20street%20all%20year%20round.%20The%20city%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnyc.streetsblog.org%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2Fchilling-effect-city-slow-to-pay-back-open-streets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslow%20to%20reimburse%20neighborhood%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20supporting%20open%20streets%20across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20estimates%2034th%20Avenue%20needs%20at%20least%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year%20to%20operate%20with%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20programming%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20City%20still%20owes%20it%20%2410%2C000%20from%20last%20year.%20The%20more%20money%20the%20street%20has%2C%20the%20more%20instructors%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20musicians%20it%20can%20pay%20to%20lead%20workshops%2C%20beautify%20the%20street%2C%20and%20put%20on%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20other%20open%20streets%20across%20the%20city%2C%2034th%20Avenue%20isn't%20a%20commercial%20street%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it's%20entirely%20residential%20in%20between%20its%20many%20schools%20and%20one%20small%20park.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20places%20that%20New%20York%20City%20has%20done%20these%20kind%20of%20more%20groundbreaking%20projects%2C%20they've%20been%20in%20wealthy%20neighborhoods%2C%26quot%3B%20Dawn%20Siff%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paseopark.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlliance%20for%20Paseo%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20supporting%20the%20open%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiff%2