0general%20manager%20of%20a%20Germany-headquartered%20pharma%20firm%20with%20wide%20operations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Visakhapatnam%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case.%20Police%20sources%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20said%20the%20case%20is%20under%20investigation%2C%20and%20they%20have%20got%20some%20leads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retired%20officer%20alleged%20some%20insiders%20in%20the%20bank%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20may%20be%20involved%2C%20as%20the%20gang%20knew%20everything%20about%20his%20account%20including%20the%20exact%20amount%20that%20he%20got%20after%20retirement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gang%20told%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20nearest%20HDFC%20Bank%20and%20drop%20the%20cheque%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fa93qr068_rana-garments-cheque_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20taken%20several%20documents%20from%20the%20HDFC%20Bank%20branch%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20bank%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20case%20when%20he%20met%20the%20bank%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHDFC%20Bank%20said%20they%20are%20cooperating%20with%20the%20Crime%20Branch.%20I%20have%20also%20told%20the%20police%2C%20was%20no%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%20done%20for%20Rana%20Garme