ge%20in%20the%20USA%2C%20Pakistan%20greats%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Waqar%20Younis%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F435-waqar-younis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWaqar%20Younis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Wasim%20Akram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F438-wasim-akram-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWasim%20Akram%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20picked%20the%20teams%20they%20believe%20would%20come%20out%20victorious.%20Despite%20Pakistan's%20poor%20form%2C%20Waqar%20feels%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20will%20take%20the%20win%20while%20Akram%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20Rohit%20Sharm'as%20team%20has%20a%20better%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20got%20off%20to%20contrasting%20starts%20in%20the%20tournament.%20While%20India%20hammered%20Ireland%20in%20their%20opener%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20stunned%20by%20co-hosts%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20says%20Pakistan%20but%20from%20what%20I've%20seen%20so%20far%20in%20this%20tournament%20the%20pitch%20in%20New%20York%20is%20very%20much%20for%20the%20faster%20bowlers.%20So%2C%20it%20evens%20it%20out%20a%20little%20bit%20just%20purely%20because%20of%20the%20surface%20in%20New%20York%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Waqar%20Younis%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkram%20feels%20India%20have%20a%2060%25%20chance%20of%20winning%20but%20things%20can%20change%20quickly%20one%20good%20innings%20or%20spell%20is%20produced%20by%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20look%20at%20India's%20form%2C%20India%20generally%20is%20a%20better%20team.%20Better%20team%20in%20a%20way%20that%20they're%20favourites%20heading%20into%20that%20game.%20I%20will%20give%2060%25%20to%20India%20and%2040%25%20to%20Pakistan.%20But%2C%20it's%20T20I%2C%20one%20good%20innings%2C%20one%20good%20spell%2C%20the%20game%20can%20change%20quickly.%20I%20think%20everybody%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20game%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Akram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20has%20always%20been%20used%20to%20evaluate%20which%20side%20will%20be%20the%20on-paper%20favourites.%20Just%20like%20other%20instances%2C%20it%20is%20favouring%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20tapped%20into%20their%20rich%20form%20just%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20While%20Pakistan's%20decision%20to%20play%20more%20cricket%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%20seems%20to%20have%20backfired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20arrived%20in%20the%20tournament%20after%20losing%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20England%20by%202-0.%20The%20losing%20momentum%20played%20ticks%20on%20their%20minds%2C%20which%20led%20to%20their%20unprecedented%20loss%20to%20the%20USA%20in%20the%20Super%20Over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20out%20of%20seven%20matches%2C%20Pakistan%20beat%20their%20arch-rival%20once.%20It%20took%20a%20spirited%20opening%20stand%20from%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20to%20take%20the%20game%20away%20from%20India%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717920480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6aarp74g_babar-and-rohit_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-wasim-akrams-big-prediction-for-t20-world-cup-clash-waqar-younis-disagrees-5851068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wasim%20Akram%20and%20Waqar%20Younis%20stood%20on%20the%20opposite%20sides%20while%20predicting%20the%20outcome%20of%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20clash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Findia-vs-pakistan-wasim-akrams-big-prediction-for-t20-world-cup-clash-waqar-you