%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMany%20Wrote%20Our%20Obituaries%26quot%3B%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20Shoutout%20To%20New%20Congress%20MPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMany%20wrote%20the%20Congress'%20obituaries%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%2C%20but%20the%20party%20has%20come%20back%20strongly%20and%20demonstrated%20its%20resilience%2C%20re-elected%20Congress%20parliamentary%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20said%2C%20congratulating%20and%20praising%20the%20newly-elected%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20party's%20parliamentary%20party%20meeting%20yesterday%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20the%20great%20responsibility%20all%20of%20you%20have%20placed%20on%20me%20yet%20again.%20Let%20me%20first%20of%20all%20greet%20and%20congratulate%20all%20the%20newly%20elected%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs.%20You%20have%20fought%20a%20tough%20election%20under%20the%20most%20challenging%20of%20circumstances.%20You%20have%20surmounted%20many%20obstacles%20and%20campaigned%20so%20very%20effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20improved%20numbers%2C%20she%20said%2C%20will%20give%20it%20a%20more%20effective%20voice%20in%20the%20Parliament's%20proceedings.%20The%20main%20Opposition%20party%20has%20won%2099%20seats%20this%20time%20--%20a%20big%20jump%20from%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2052.%20%26quot%3BYour%20success%20has%20given%20us%20a%20much%2C%20much%20greater%20presence%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20a%20more%20effective%20voice%20in%20its%20proceedings%2C%20both%20of%20which%20will%20help%20give%20greater%20strength%20to%20our%20participation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20up%20against%20%26quot%3Ba%20mighty%20and%20malevolent%20machine%20that%20was%20doing%20its%20utmost%20to%20destroy%20us%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20tried%20to%20cripple%20us%20financially.%20It%20carried%20out%20a%20campaign%20against%20us%20and%20our%20leaders%20that%20was%20full%20of%20lies%20and%20defamation.%20Many%20wrote%20our%20obituaries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20under%20the%20determined%20leadership%20of%20Kharge%20ji%20we%20persevered.%20He%20is%20an%20inspiration%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20His%20commitment%20to%20the%20party%20organisation%20and%20its%20ideology%20is%20truly%20extraordinary%20and%20we%20all%20have%20to%20learn%20from%20his%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20praising%20the%20veteran%20party%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20role%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20yatras%20played%20in%20the%20Congress's%20performance%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20were%20historic%20movements%20which%20rejuvenated%20our%20party%20at%20all%20levels.%20Rahul%20deserves%20special%20thanks%20for%20his%20tenacity%20and%20determination%20to%20fight%20on%20in%20the%20face%20of%20unprecedented%20personal%20and%20political%20attacks.%20He%20also%20shaped%20our%20narrative%20on%20guarantees%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20Constitution%20very%20sharply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20my%20personal%20belief%20that%20the%20constant%20upholding%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20our%20Constitution%20during%20our%20campaigns%20by%20Rahul%20and%20Kharge%20ji%2C%20and%20all%20of%20you%20is%20that%20which%20compelled%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20yesterday%20to%20bow%20down%20literally%20to%20that%20which%20for%20us%20is%20a%20precious%20book%2C%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20Congress%20workers%20across%20the%20country%20for%20their%20hard%20work%20in%20the%20party's%20campaign%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOurs%20has%20also%20been%20a%20campaign%20where%20we%20have%20functioned%20truly%20as%20a%20collective.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%20also%20praised%20Congress%20candidates%20who%20could%20not%20win%20the%20polls%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthey%20fought%20valiantly%20and%20did%20our%20party%20proud%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Gandhi%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20party%20has%20challenging%20times%20ahead.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20alert%20to%20prevent%20any%20attempts%20to%20increase%20polarisation%20and%20erosion%20of%20secular%20and%20democratic%20values.%20This%20is%20a%20renewed%20opportunity%20for%20us%20as%20a%20party%20that%20established%20parliamentary%20democracy%20in%20our%20country%20to%20bring%20parliamentary%20politics%20back%20on%20track%20to%20where%20they%20legitimately%20belong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20election%2C%20the%20people%20have%20voted%20decisively%20to%20reject%20the%20politics%20of%20divisiveness%20and%20authoritarianism.%20They%20have%20voted%20to%20strengthen%20parliamentary%20politics%20and%20safeguard%20our%20Constitution.%20They%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20agenda%20of%20economic%20and%20social%20justice%20that%20indeed%20should%20continue%20to%20be%20our%20objective%20and%20guide%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717920000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fafmfo2qg_sonia-gandhi-kharge_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-congress-many-wrote-our-obituaries-sonia-gandhis-shoutout-to-new-congress-mps-5851014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20wrote%20the%20Congress'%20obituaries%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%2C%20but%20the%20party%20has%20come%20back%20strongly%20and%20demonstrated%20its%20resilence%2C%20Congress%20parliamentary%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%20this%20afternoon%2C%20congratulating%20and%20praising%20the%20newly-elected%20MPs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-congress-many-wrote-our-obituaries-sonia-gandhis-shoutout-to-new-congress-mps-5851014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppro