i%20Mankermi%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20vs%20Pakistan%20Pitch%20Report%3A%20Do%20Rohit's%20Men%20Really%20Have%20The%20Edge%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20of%20us%20might%20have%20come%20out%20of%20the%20shell%20after%20what%20happened%20in%20Dallas%20on%20June%206.%20The%20USA%20stunned%20an%20off-coloured%20Pakistan%20side%20via%20a%20Super%20Over%20win%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20upsets%20in%20cricket's%20history.%20After%20that%20shocking%20debacle%2C%20Babar%20Azam's%20unit%20is%20up%20for%20another%20daunting%20challenge%20and%20this%20time%20against%20their%20arch-rivals%20India.%20Their%20head-to-head%20battle%20against%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20tilts%20towards%20the%20latter%20though%20with%20five%20wins%20out%20of%20seven%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20India%20will%20be%20entering%20the%20contest%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20comfortable%20win%20against%20Ireland%20by%20eight%20wickets%20and%20what%20could%20be%20more%20satisfying%20than%20skipper%20Rohit%20(52%20off%2037)%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20(3%2F27)%20returning%20to%20form%20ahead%20of%20a%20blockbuster%20outing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20bowling%20unit%20looks%20more%20confident%20after%20the%20likes%20of%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20and%20Pandya%20have%20delivered%20fruitful%20returns%20with%20the%20ball%20in%20their%20tournament%20opener.%20The%20redemption%20of%20Rishabh%20Pant%20at%20No.3%20has%20also%20allowed%20Virat%20Kohli%20to%20open%20the%20proceedings%20with%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%2C%20India's%20superstar%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20does%20not%20need%20any%20introduction%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Pakistan.%20The%2035-year-old%20has%20smashed%20308%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20132.8%20against%20the%20Men%20in%20Green.%20Hopefully%2C%20if%20he%20gets%20going%20on%20Sunday%20then%20there's%20looking%20back%20for%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20India's%20batting%20has%20the%20luxury%20of%20four%20left-hand%20batters%20-%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20Shivam%20Dube%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20and%20Axar%20Patel.%20Their%20form%20with%20the%20bat%20will%20be%20the%20key%20to%20India's%20success%20in%20the%20lower%20middle%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pakistan%20have%20produced%20sloppy%20performances%20in%20their%20previous%20few%20T20I%20matches.%20An%20away-series%20loss%20against%20England%20has%20also%20exposed%20their%20loopholes%20early%20in%20the%20season.%20Their%20old-school%20style%20of%20cricket%20immediately%20needs%20a%20software%20update%20if%20they%20want%20to%20make%20a%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20batting%20led%20by%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20has%20been%20performing%20in%20bits%20and%20pieces%20and%20the%20ICC%20tournaments%20demand%20positive%20intent%20from%20the%20batters%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unpredictable%20side%20has%20also%20been%20inconsistent%20in%20their%20team%20selections.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20they%20brought%20back%20their%20alumni%20Mohammad%20Amir%20and%20Imad%20Wasim%20out%20of%20retirement%20to%20join%20their%20core%20group.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20also%20roped%20in%20Usman%20Khan%20into%20their%20squad%2C%20who%20used%20to%20play%20for%20UAE%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20comebacks%20didn't%20make%20a%20difference%20either%20and%20a%20struggling%20Azam%20Khan%20also%20threw%20challenges%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20Men%20in%20Green%20have%20also%20appointed%20the%20South%20African%20veteran%20Gary%20Kirsten%20as%20their%20T20%20coach%20ahead%20of%20the%20ICC%20event.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20too%20early%20to%20judge%20Gary%20as%20a%20coach%20considering%20he%20won%20an%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20with%20India%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20a%20collective%20effort%20from%20Pakistan%20can%20only%20help%20them%20dominate%20India%20at%20the%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20the%20pitches%20at%20Nassau%20County%20offer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20matches%20so%20far%20at%20the%20Nassau%20County%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%2C%20only%20one%20batter%20has%20been%20able%20to%20register%20a%20half-century%20-%20Rohit%20Sharma%20scored%2052%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20excessive%20seam%20movement%20and%20bounce%2C%20batters%20were%20getting%20hit%20by%20the%20ball%2C%20and%20conditions%20have%20been%20anything%20but%20standard%20in%20New%20York.%20These%20conditions%20forced%20India%20to%20start%20with%20three%20genuine%20pacers%20and%20two%20spin-bowling%20all-rounders%20in%20Jadeja%20and%20Axar%20instead%20of%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20pitch%20and%20conditions%2C%20we%20are%20open%20to%20make%20changes%20and%20do%20what%20is%20required%20at%20that%20point%2C%20but%20today%20was%20a%20four-seamer%20pitch%20and%20we%20still%20managed%20to%20get%20two%20spinners%2C%20who%20are%20all-rounders.%20It%20gives%20us%20balance%20heading%20into%20the%20game.%20It%20%5BPakistan%20game%5D%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20kind%20of%20game%20where%20all%20of%20us%20need%20to%20contribute%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20after%20India%20humbled%20Ireland%20on%20June%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20preparations%20are%20concerned%2C%20India%20will%20prepare%20for%20tough%20batting%20conditions%20when%20they%20play%20Pakistan%20on%20Sunday.%20However%2C%20this%20might%20come%20as%20a%20boon%20for%20Pakistani%20pacers%2C%20who%20have%20dismantled%20India's%20batting%20in%20the%20past%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%