20to%20lead%20all%20AI%2FAutopilot%20software.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWithout%20him%20and%20our%20awesome%20team%2C%20we%20would%20just%20be%20another%20car%20company%20looking%20for%20an%20autonomy%20supplier%20that%20doesn't%20exist.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBtw%2C%20I%20never%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7eBfzu0Nci%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7eBfzu0Nci%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1799650788848841069%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAshok%20Elluswamy%2C%20in%20his%20detailed%20note%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CElon%20Musk%20has%20been%20the%20key%20driver%20of%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20at%20Tesla.%20He%20has%20always%20pushed%20us%20to%20achieve%20great%20things%2C%20even%20when%20such%20ideas%20were%20seemingly%20impossible%20at%20the%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Ashok%20also%20talked%20about%20an%20instance%20that%20goes%20back%20to%202014%2C%20when%20%E2%80%9Cautopilot%20started%20on%20a%20ridiculously%20tiny%20computer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20in%202014%2C%20Autopilot%20started%20on%20a%20ridiculously%20tiny%20computer%20that%20only%20had%20~384%20KB%20of%20memory%20and%20puny%20compute%20(didn't%20even%20have%20native%20floating-point%20arithmetic).%20He%20%5BElon%20Musk%5D%20asked%20the%20engineering%20team%20to%20implement%20lane%20keeping%2C%20lane%20changing%2C%20longitudinal%20control%20for%20vehicles%2C%20curvature%2C%20etc.%20Many%2C%20even%20in%20the%20team%2C%20thought%20that%20the%20request%20was%20crazy.%20Nonetheless%2C%20he%20never%20gave%20up%20and%20pushed%20the%20team%20to%20achieve%20this%20very%20difficult%20goal.%20In%202015%2C%20beyond%20all%20odds%2C%20Tesla%20shipped%20the%20world's%20first%20Autopilot%20system.%20The%20second%20closest%20such%20product%20only%20came%20to%20market%20many%20years%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Ashok%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202016%2C%20Tesla%20started%20doing%20all%20of%20the%20computer%20vision%20required%20for%20Autopilot%20in-house%20instead%20of%20depending%20on%20external%20vendors.%20Many%20people%20thought%20it%20was%20insane%20to%20bet%20the%20product%20on%20developing%20the%20vision%20system%20from%20scratch%20within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20which%20had%20taken%20other%20companies%20a%20decade%20or%20more.%20Yet%2C%20we%20achieved%20this%20target%20within%20eleven%20months.%20This%20was%20a%20strategically%20important%20move%20that%20started%20the%20development%20of%20a%20strong%20AI%20team%20at%20Tesla.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELauding%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20he%20push%20for%20strong%20AI%20software%2C%20but%20also%20for%20powerful%20AI%20hardware.%20Tesla%2C%20which%20others%20thought%20was%20just%20a%20car%20company%2C%20was%20making%20custom%20silicon%20to%20run%20neural%20networks%20efficiently.%20This%20hardware%20that%20was%20originally%20designed%20in%202017%2C%20came%20to%20production%20in%20February%202019%20and%20remains%20extremely%20competitive%20with%20hardware%20coming%20out%20to%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BElon%20Musk%5D%20was%20the%20one%20who%20bet%20on%20vision%20and%20AI%20to%20solve%20autonomy%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20sensor%20crutches%20and%20high-definition%20maps.%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Ashok%20noted%20that%20by%20shipping%20millions%20of%20Teslas%20the%20company%20has%20proved%20all%20of%20them%20wrong%2C%20who%20used%20to%20ridicule%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Ashok%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20back%20in%202020%20and%20earlier%20it%20wasn't%20obvious%20to%20most.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20%26quot%3Bexperts%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20field%20ridiculed%20Tesla%20and%20Elon%20for%20these%20choices.%20We%20have%20proved%20them%20wrong%20by%20shipping%20supervised%20FSD%20to%20millions%20of%20cars%20and%20shown%20that%20with%20good%20AI%20software%2C%20the%20car%20is%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20complexities%20of%20city%20driving%20such%20as%20making%20turns%2C%20handling%20intersections%2C%20yielding%20to%20pedestrians%20etc.%2C%20just%20by%20seeing%20outside.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20even%20removed%20the%20radars%20and%20ultrasonics%20to%20just%20really%20focus%20on%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20which%20is%20AI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BElon%20Musk%5D%20kickstarted%20the%20work%20on%20humanoid%20robots%20at%20Tesla%20in%202021%2C%20again%20before%20any%20ChatGPT%20or%20other%20obvious%20examples%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20AI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Ashok%20concluded%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20go%20on%2C%20but%20plainly%2C%20Elon%20is%20critical%20for%20Tesla's%20success%20in%20AI.%20It%20is%20his%20combination%20of%20deep%20technical%20understanding%2C%20insane%20perseverance%20and%20relentless%20hard%20work%20that%20have%20positioned%20Tesla%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20real-world%20AI.%20Elon's%20technical%20intuition%20to%20make%20these%20important%20decisions%20way%20before%20others%20see%20it%20is%20unmatched.%20If%20not%20for%20Elon's%20ambition%2C%20Tesla%20might%20have%20dwindled%20to%20become%20just%20another%20car%20company.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20fully%20autonomous%20cars%20and%20useful%20household%20robots%20will%20be%20commonplace%20and%20the%20world%20will%20think%20that%20this%20was%20how%20it%20was%20always%20supposed%20to%20be.%20Until%20then%2C%20we%20need%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20push%20the%20frontier%2C%20because%20he%20sees%20it%20already.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ERead%20his%20complete%20post%20here%3A%3C%2F