ious%20and%20no%20one%20found%20dignity%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257903%2Futtarakhand-startup-himshakti-pahadi-namak-pink-salt-harshit-sahdev-ancient-food-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20salts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20family%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction%20and%20that%20I%20was%20possessed%20by%20some%20hill%20ghost!%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20believed%20me%20only%20after%20six%20months%20when%20my%20work%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20news.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%2C%20are%20buying%20luxurious%20cars.%20Often%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20them%20and%20earn%20handsome%20salaries.%20But%20here%2C%20when%20I%20see%20happy%20families%20getting%20financial%20independence%20through%20our%20work%2C%20it%20motivates%20me%20to%20work%20further.%20No%20other%20achievement%20could%20give%20us%20the%20contentment%20we%20experience%20through%20this%20work.%20Every%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20well%20knowing%2080%20families%20are%20sleeping%20peacefully%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20HimFla.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716976330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-2-1716968175.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351421%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandeep%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20of%20opening%20a%20restaurant%20were%20shattered%20by%20the%202013%20Uttarakhand%20floods.%20Later%2C%20with%20his%20childhood%20friends%20Sourabh%20Pant%20and%20Yogendra%20Singh%2C%20he%20founded%20HimFla%2C%20a%20startup%20selling%20Uttarakhand's%20traditional%20%E2%80%98pahadi%E2%80%99%20salt.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22h